{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "flight-runway-scheduler-001",
    "name": "Flight Runway Scheduler API",
    "description": "API collection for the Flight Runway Scheduling System (TypeScript + Event-Driven).\n\n## Architecture\n- Event-driven scheduler using Node.js EventEmitter\n- Pluggable scheduling strategies (FIFO, EmergencyFirst, LandingPriority, Balanced)\n- Services emit events: flight:created, flight:updated, flight:cancelled, runway:released, runway:enabled/disabled\n- Scheduler listens to events and auto-assigns flights to available runways\n\n## Logging\nServer logs show: [flight queued], [scheduler triggered], [runway assigned], [flight completed], etc.\n\n## Endpoints (unchanged from v1)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Flights",
      "description": "Flight management endpoints",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Flight",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"flightNumber\": \"AI203\",\n  \"airline\": \"Air India\",\n  \"type\": \"landing\",\n  \"emergency\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/flights",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["flights"]
            },
            "description": "Create a new flight request. Type can be 'landing' or 'takeoff'. Emergency is optional (defaults to false)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Emergency Flight",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"flightNumber\": \"EMRG01\",\n  \"airline\": \"Emergency Services\",\n  \"type\": \"landing\",\n  \"emergency\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:3000/flights",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["localhost"],
              "port": "3000",
              "path": ["flights"]
            },
            "description": "Create an emergency flight that gets priority in the queue."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
